cale of the time to reach\nconsensus, based on the analysis of the underlying structural properties of\nopinion spreading.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2016 09:26:00 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Jun 2016 05:50:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 28 May 2017 08:32:35 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 9 Jun 2017 21:18:12 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 13 Jun 2017 01:41:19 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Mon, 9 Apr 2018 15:57:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-10"}
