agree for the\ndecoupled phase with weak exchange $J1$ between sublattices. Two related models\nare summarized: one has an exact gapless decoupled phase with QLRO({$\\pi$}/2)\nand no IC phases; the other has a single IC phase without a decoupled phase in\nbetween.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Mar 2016 15:19:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-20"}
